LIMITED EDITION
This new model marks the 2019 25th birthday of the BABY-G watch for active women with a design that revives the look of the very first BABY-G (DW-520). The case and band are made of semi-transparent resin material and the face feature a protector against external shock that also creates a retro 90s feel. The logo of this model is a single "G" character, and blue, purple, and pink colors are combined to recreate the look of the original model.
The back cover of this model is impressed with a special logo to commemorate the BABY-G 25th anniversary. Packaging also sports this logo along with a street style cool design.
This new model is a great way to celebrate the 25th memorial year of the BABY-G.
